Declaring JSON Variable:

name json;

JSON - stores key-value pairs of data

JSON-specific operations:

json_each() - expand JSON object into a set of key-value pairs
json_array_elements() - expands JSON array into a set of JSON values
-> - extracts JSON objects by key
->> - extracts JSON objects by key and returns text

e.g.:

SELECT info ->> 'customer' AS customer_name
FROM orders;
